title: Am I Overthinking It Or Am I Crazy?
itunes:title: Am I Overthinking It Or Am I Crazy?
description:
Brooke and Danielle get into some pretty heavy feelings while going over recent relationship/business decisions. They also discuss how important it is to be in tune with those emotions and be able to express them during a time like this.
